Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah berlatih di rumah Arel...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}selama tiga tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keahlian menyeduh tehmu\Nmeningkat pesat, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.89,0:00:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini semua berkat bimbinganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mira?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat aku mau membangunkan Abang,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di sana hanya ada surat ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.22,0:00:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan pergi ke Kota Sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Abang pergi lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah, sudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memang bilang tertarik\Ndengan Kota Sihir,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi ini tiba-tiba, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.59,0:01:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pernah melakukan hal serupa\Ndengan keluargaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.51,0:01:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi begini rasanya\Ntiba-tiba ditinggalkan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi Reiner, jangan tiba-tiba\Nmenghilang dari kami, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak akan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masih banyak yang ingin kupelajari darimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Si Mbak dan anak itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang di keluarga kami\Nagak terlalu bebas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku penasaran mereka mirip siapa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.77,0:01:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, yang penting semuanya baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berapa lama lagi kita tiba di Kota Sihir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin dua hari lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, kamu cukup aneh, ya, Tuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiga tahun lalu,\Nkamu mengguncang Kota Pedang,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi setelah itu, kamu langsung pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kali ini kamu akan pergi ke Kota Sihir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, kamu juga akan pergi ke Institut Sihir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, kamu tampak\Njauh lebih tua dari kami, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya sudah terlambat bagimu\Nuntuk masuk Institut Sihir?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin dia sering gagal ujian masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bekerja keras untuk itu,\Njadi jangan mengejeknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kufa, kamu terdengar mendukungnya,\Ntapi malah mengejeknya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak seperti itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jangan bertengkar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam, Collette!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak peduli dengan gadis seperti dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga tidak peduli dengan bocah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa?\N- Dasar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa mereka semua penyihir?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, mereka terlihat\Nbaru saja menerima berkat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, sihir apa yang kamu kuasai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, spesialisasiku sihir merah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihir yang kukuasai, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengar, Arel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihir terbagi menjadi beberapa sifat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihir terbagi menjadi beberapa sifat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Merah, biru, hijau,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kuning, putih, dan hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Totalnya enam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski kemampuan sihir yang bisa diperoleh\Nberbeda tiap orangnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk kasusmu,\Ntidak ada batasan seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita coba semua sihir yang kutahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, kita mulai yang mana dulu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm, aku tidak ada keahlian khusus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, aku Tanpa Kelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kaito, dia bercanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya, Tanpa Kelas\Ntidak akan mau masuk Institut Sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, jangan membuat lelucon payah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak berbohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini, Kartu Kelasku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Tidak mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kali pertama aku melihat Tanpa Kelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu Tanpa Kelas\Ndan betulan ingin belajar sihir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sudah gila?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pernah merasakan situasi seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mendengar suara keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu raungan Raja Troll.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya dia mengaum\Nke arah kita dari hutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Raja Troll?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu monster yang sangat kuat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Paman, ayo pergi dari sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua kuda pingsan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita akan mati!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang, Collette.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Raja atau bukan, Troll hanyalah Troll.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka badannya besar,\Npasti geraknya lambat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serangan kita pasti akan kena.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau bekerja sama, mungkin berhasil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo keluarkan semua sihir kita\Ndan kalahkan mereka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh! Kalau takut, kamu kalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memang besar,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi makhluk itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:06:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu terlalu besar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makhluk apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil kita bisa menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bukan lawan yang bisa kita hadapi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan sihirku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menolak mati tanpa melakukan apa pun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kugunakan semua energi sihirku,\Npasti berhasil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fireball!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhasil! Serangan langsung.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dampaknya nol!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu hanya membuatnya marah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kehabisan sihir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Raja Troll menjadi abu dalam sekejap?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harusnya aku mengurangi kekuatannya lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu jelas berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan,\Nbarusan kamu yang melakukannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Collette, kalau tidak salah,\NExplosion itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihir Merah tingkat tertinggi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, bukankah itu sihir\Nyang dipakai kelas Penyihir Agung?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kali ini, kamu menyelamatkanku lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lain kali, aku ingin melihat kemampuanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga tidak ada masalah seperti itu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Anu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku minta maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahu kamu Guru Senior!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf atas kelancanganku tadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bukan guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai sekarang,\Nizinkan aku memanggilmu Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin menjadi penyihir hebat sepertimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kubilang, aku bukan orang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu ingin melihat\NKartu Tanpa Kelasku lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kartu itu pasti palsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, kamu menyembunyikan\Nidentitas aslimu karena suatu alasan, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Master memang hebat, kamu keren!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, sudah kubilang.\NAku ini Tanpa Kelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, semuanya.\NKita lanjut perjalanan ke Kota Sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harusnya tadi aku menggunakan pedangku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pulau yang mengapung di danau itu\Nadalah Kota Sihir, Alsbel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, seperti kata Ayah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempatnya cukup menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Konon jembatan ini juga\Nditopang dengan sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat terasa seperti Kota Sihir, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Si Kaito yang songong menempel\Npadanya seperti anak anjing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu Arel memiliki sihir hebat,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku masih terkejut.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bilang dia pakai sihir\Nuntuk menjinakkannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita amati dari kejauhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia membuat kesalahpahaman\Nyang tidak perlu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Master juga akan ikut\Nujian masuk Institut Merah, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa institut juga dibagi\Nberdasarkan tipe sihir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena bahasa, kosakata,\Ndan tata bahasa sihir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berbeda tergantung pada sifat sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan pergi ke Institut Biru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan pergi ke Institut Hijau.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat gugup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hati-hati, atau nanti diusir\Ndan dikirim kembali ke pedesaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan membalas kata-kata itu padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ujian masuk, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga aku tidak ditolak lagi\Nseperti saat di Kota Pedang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua peserta ujian,\Nisi formulir pendaftarannya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan serahkan ke meja resepsionis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Master, itu meja resepsionis\Nuntuk ujian masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arel, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kampung halaman, Feighnott.\NKelasnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa semua informasinya benar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi Tanpa Kelas juga\Ntidak boleh berpartisipasi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua informasimu sudah lengkap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nomor peserta ujianmu 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Tanpa Kelas boleh berpartisipasi juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:12:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa pun kelasmu,\Nkamu berhak mengikuti ujian.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sangat berbeda dari Kota Pedang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, Master, ayo ke tempat ujian!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan kemampuan Master,\Nkamu pasti akan langsung lulus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fireball!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kena!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nomor 10, kamu lulus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikutnya, Nomor 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang menggunakan Fireball dasar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada kerennya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masih sangat muda,\Nsudah jadi penyihir Kelas Lanjutan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serius?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu hal hebat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk diberkati dengan Kelas Lanjutan,\Nsudah pasti dia genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu jalan elite, jalan mulus menuju sukses\Nyang membuat siapa pun iri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diberkati dengan Kelas Lanjutan, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi seseorang juga bisa berakhir\Nsebagai pria tua biasa di pedesaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:13:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku boleh menggunakan apiku\Nuntuk menghancurkan bonekanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Master, pria itu terlihat songong, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa kamu tidak berhak bicara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terbakarlah menjadi abu!\NEruption!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat! Itu pilar api!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi itu penyihir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia betulan\Npeserta ujian seperti kita?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, dia lumayan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dia tidak sehebat Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bisa pura-pura\Ntidak mendengar itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu mastermu setara denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh, dia lebih kuat darimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, kan, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya mastermu mengerti\Nperbedaan kekuatan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melelehkan logam dengan api sepertiku,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu bukan hal yang bisa dilakukan\Npenyihir biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berbaliklah dan lihat baik-baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak meleleh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa bertahan dari Eruption-ku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:14:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu boneka mitril\Nyang dibuat Institut Kuning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak akan meleleh semudah itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mitril?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bahan yang lebih keras\Ndaripada bijih lainnya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.17,0:14:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kota Sihir memang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu terdengar sangat percaya diri,\Ntapi payah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau masterâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan libatkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikutnya, Nomor 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kamu terus membual\Nlebih kuat dariku,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tunjukkan sihirmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bilang apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja! Bersiaplah menyaksikan\Nsihir terhebat masterku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kali pertamaku\Nmenggunakan sihir pada mitril.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mumpung ada kesempatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saatnya serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eruption!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Barusan itu apaan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:15:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya melihat\Nsekilas pilar api setipis jarum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sangat tidak mengesankan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti komedi saja, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sampai tertawa puas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin Master akan gagal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mitrilnya betulan meleleh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia berhasil!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu curang!\NEruption tidak bisa melelehkan mitril!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, sebenarnya ini bukan Eruption biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini teknik dengan menekan jangkauan api\Ndan menyesuaikan waktu erupsinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu memodifikasi sihirmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana mungkin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu luar biasa, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan melakukan yang terbaik setelahmu.\NTolong lihat aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mau ke mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke tempat ujian berikutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Water Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kena!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, kamu lulus?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk mengikuti ujian.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Bukankah kamu sudah pergi\Nke Institut Merah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.11,0:16:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ice Edge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boneka mitrilnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, berikutnya Institut Hijau.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kuduga, aku tidak bisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Collette?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Arel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedang apa di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bilang kamu gagal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, saking gugupnya, kakiku gemetaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahkan belum mendaftar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tipe orang\Nyang tidak bisa tampil saat gugup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka berdua selalu membantuku selama ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi untuk ujian,\Nkamu harus berjuang sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu, bagaimana kamu bisa tenang\Nsaat merasa gugup?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayangnya, aku belum pernah merasa gugup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tahu sedikit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tentang kondisi abnormal\Nsaat tidak bisa bergerak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebaliknya, aku ingin tanya\Nkenapa kamu bisa gugup?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa alasannya karena gelisah\Natau takut gagal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku bertanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Collette, kamu tidak pernah gagal\Ndalam hidupmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, justru sebaliknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu gagal,\Njadi aku ingin menghindarinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga selalu gagal dan kalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu setakut ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mengerti maksudmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.39,0:17:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalam kebanyakan situasi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hidupmu tidak akan berakhir\Nkarena satu kegagalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, ujian masuk\Ntidak boleh mengancam nyawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau itu bisa membunuh orang?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski gagal, aku tidak akan mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku masih bisa mencoba lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Intinya begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa termotivasi lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, iya, ujian Institut Hijau tentang apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar orang akan lulus...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalau membuat kincir angin\Ndi tempat ujian berputar dengan sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.34,0:18:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kincir anginnya hancur berkeping-keping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Itu bukan mitril,\Ntapi terbuat dari kayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nomor 15, kamu lulus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Peserta ujian berikutnya,\Nsilakan gunakan kincir angin sebelah sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:19:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus tampil setelah\Npertunjukan sihir yang luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hidupmu tidak akan berakhir\Nkarena satu kegagalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nomor 16, memulai ujian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ujian masuk Kuning dan Putih\Njuga berjalan lancar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya Institut Hitam yang tersisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini seperti reruntuhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana Gooey?\NKamu lihat Gooey-ku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:19:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gooey hilang!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mendengar suara dari kotak ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gooey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gooey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Si kecil ini adalah Chimera\Nyang kuciptakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia manis, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum pernah melihatmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang di Institut Sihir Hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu kejam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiba-tiba memenggal kepala seorang wanita!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kamu monster Undead?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.47,0:20:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, aku Latalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti yang kamu lihat,\Naku staf yang cantik.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dilihat dari mana pun, dia cuma kerangka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Latalia, tolong beri tahu aku,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di mana ujian Institut Hitam diadakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak ada ujian masuk di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada cukup anak\Nyang ingin belajar sihir hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, semua orang diterima di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu yakin menerimaku sesantai ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gooey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, sepertinya benar\Nsiapa pun diterima di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya kami menemukanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa dengan kalian bertiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Master akan memilih Merah, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, Biru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah pasti Hijau.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kalian bicarakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tentang institut yang akan Master pilih!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jelas Merah, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mulai dengan ujian Institut Merah\Nuntuk menunjukkan itu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.61,0:21:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kubilang Biru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia ingin menunjukkan presisi\Ndan kekuatan sihir esnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, itu sama dengan tornadonya\Nyang menghancurkan kincir angin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak akan memilih satu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.29,0:21:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.06,0:21:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menghadiri semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan untuk Master sekalipun,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}masuk ke tiga sekolah sendirian\Nagak berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:21:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku ikut enam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:21:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Merah, Biru, Hijau,\NKuning, Putih, dan Hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menghadiri semua institusi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?